OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy and mostly dry through the
OL,7,Fevening and overnight. A few outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain possible however, with these
OL,9,Fmainly in the west. Winds easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAnother cloudy and mostly dry
OL,12,Fday with a few spells of light rain
OL,13,Fpossible in the north and west. Some
OL,14,Foccasional bright spells in the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,17,Fdry and cloudy Monday and Tuesday with
OL,18,Fa few outbreaks of rain in the north
OL,19,Fand west and some brightness in the
OL,20,Fsoutheast. Dry Wednesday with bright
OL,21,Fspells developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
